reviews.review_text: Short show This show is one minute over two hours. Quite short for the time, especially the 2nd set.

Just amazing Playin in the Band This Playing is the definition of late era HEAVY Grateful Dead. It's  absolutely the best version until 5/26/93. Both are great examples of "Jerry going off". If you like Jerry taking the lead you will love this. 

Also take a look at Jerry "going off" during the UJB jam from 2/27/94 if you're interested in Jerry playing unusual music.
